        "description": "The player must survive and expel evil spirits from their entire house. Turn your house into a horror game and experience evil spirits that will hunt you down. The Spirts will be able to navigate your physical environment.  There are up to 10 evil spirts you can avoid, each with a unique ability and hunting style.\n\nImportant: Make sure you restart your headset after downloading to fix any tracking issues.  \n\nMixed Reality Boundaries will be removed in the next update for the average player and Hauntify will follow Meta's new multi-room system making it much easier to setup.  \n\nQuest 1 is not supported!\n\nIf you need help with the setup or have feedback, join our Discord page on the company website!  \n\nThis game will go through a massive update this summer/fall.  Setup will be improved and a lot easier for all headsets.  This is current early access and experimental, but your support will help this game grow and improve. \n\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/53d4NQnDE9\n",
